ai-patthana14.11:0.2_0: The Order of the Dhamma ladies that are difficult for the living, etc.,
ai-patthana14.11:2.1_1: Excellent Teaching arises in the world. The Teaching does not give rise to the best cause.
ai-patthana14.11:2.1_2: Thoughts that arise in the supermundane, and the supermundane faculties don’t arise.
ai-patthana14.11:3.1_0: For the sake of looking at supermundane, the supramundane Dhamma arises dependent on the north.
ai-patthana14.11:4.1_0: ‘... for the sake of all five hundred objects, five hundred objects, namely, this five hundred objects.’ ...
